/************************************************************
 * 09_BUDGET.gs - Intelligent Dynamic Budget System
 * 
 * Advanced budget management to maximize use of 30s limit:
 * - Real-time budget allocation
 * - Adaptive thresholds based on remaining time
 * - Phase-based execution (Discovery, Balance, Price, Output)
 * - Predictive time estimation
 * 
 * v4.15.14 - QUOTA-AWARE BUDGET: DynamicBudget.selectProfile now factors
 *   remaining HTTP quota into profile selection (not just execution time).
 *   - Quota <5%  → HIBERNATED (cache-only, no token HTTP)
 *   - Quota <15% → MINIMAL max (3 tokens, 1 price lookup)
 *   - Quota <40% → CONSERVATIVE max (5 tokens, 2 price lookups)
 *   - Quota ≥40% → time-based selection (normal behavior)
 *
 * v4.12.32 - CRITICAL FIX: ScriptProperties instead of SheetCache
 * - FIXED: ChainBudgetStats now uses ScriptProperties (not SheetCache)
 * - SheetCache.setValues() fails from formulas: "permission denied"
 * - ScriptProperties works from formulas without permission issues
 * - Maintains same data structure and TTL logic
 *
 * v4.12.30 - CRITICAL FIX: ChainBudgetStats key collision
 * - FIXED: All chains used same key 'DYNAMIC_BUDGET_STATS_CHAIN'
 * - NOW: Unique key per chain 'DYNAMIC_BUDGET_STATS_ChainName'
 * - Prevents stats being overwritten between chains
 *
 * v4.12.29 - INTERVAL ALIGNMENT FOR 2H REFRESH CYCLE:
 * - Updated fallback intervals: scan=8h (was 1h), price=6h (was 6h)
 * - Aligned with WCORE_CACHE_CONFIG changes in 01_INIT.gs
 *
 * (Changelog v4.5.0..v4.12.13: 11 entries removed for brevity)
 ************************************************************/

