/**
 * BudgetStats v4.6.0 - NO LONGER PERSISTS DATA
 * 
 * All methods return empty/default values to maintain API compatibility
 * but NO data is written to ScriptProperties.
 * 
 * This saves ~9KB of storage (previously 63 entries @ ~150 bytes each)
